agak tak stabil.

718
00:35:37,159 --> 00:35:38,959
Lebih baik jangan biar
dia ketahui penyakitnya

719
00:35:39,120 --> 00:35:40,600
untuk meringankan bebannya.

720
00:35:41,600 --> 00:35:42,959
Baik. Terima kasih, doktor.

721
00:35:43,159 --> 00:35:44,239
Sama-sama.

722
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:03,919
Fanlu.

723
00:36:04,879 --> 00:36:06,399
Kalau awak benar-benar ditimpa malang,

724
00:36:07,280 --> 00:36:09,040
